info.author: Maarten van Gompel
classifiers: License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License v3 (GPLv3)
info.keywords: nlp computational_linguistics rest database document server
info.name: foliadocserve
info.summary: The FoLiA Document Server is a backend HTTP service to interact with documents in the FoLiA format, a rich XML-based format for linguistic annotation (http://proycon.github.io/folia). It provides an interface to efficiently edit FoLiA documents through the FoLiA Query Language (FQL).
